It's so simple. as the title says, create a nickname for the person above you. Just complete the sentence "I dub thee, _______". You may explain why, but it's optional.

Ex: i dub thee, mmbmc, guardian of the chaos tavern.

My topic rules:
Follow the Forum rules
Be nice to others
Don't spam my thread
No double post. (self gratification is not a cool thing to do)
Have fun! (yes, that's an order!)
and last but not the least, ladyamethyst-is-so-cool-and-there's-noth ing-you-could-do-about-it! *cough*


so, let's play!
